imming.\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}, {\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9945902284109462, \"rank\": 0.004656919283415977, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her faith\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"the anti-doping system\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"an all-time low\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 417}, {\"ngram\": \"the widely-criticized handling\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"failed drug tests\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In excerpts from an interview with \\\"CBS News Sunday Morning\\\" that will air this weekend, Ledecky spoke about the 23 Chinese swimmers who avoided sanctions after testing positive for a banned substance months before the Tokyo Olympics held in 2021.\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News_Sunday_Morning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CBS News Sunday Morning\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News_Sunday_Morning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News_Sunday_Morning\"}, {\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9945902284109462, \"rank\": 0.004656919283415977, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wik